{"tid":216374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"牛角 推出AA祭二人餐＄496","createTime":"2017-04-25T06:25:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T09:03:32.000Z","uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5252a84172a203afe30138b97e01a17227ff8a6","tid":216374,"uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:25:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170425&amp;guid=56610340&amp;category_guid=10829392&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170425%26guid%3D56610340%26category_guid%3D10829392%26category%3Dinstant&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5gHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=faba23f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170425%26guid%3D56610340%26category_guid%3D10829392%26category%3Dinstant&h=0ba047ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170425&amp;guid=56610340&amp;category_guid=10829392&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170425/large/1493097482_42ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170425%2Flarge%2F1493097482_42ae.jpg&h=71feb3e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連牛角老闆黃傑龍都要親自喺facebook出post解畫，呢餐飯非常厲害！點知一波未平一波又起，「牛角」轉個頭又嚟多個靚抽，推出「網燒真戀人．AA祭二人餐」，盛惠$496，記住！記住！記住！AA制每位只係要$248咋。個餐有乜食？有和牛牛肋肉、上級牛肋肉、豬頸肉、前菜及飲品兩杯等。當然唔少得張2,000蚊賬單上嘅重點──獺祭三割九分純米大吟釀，不過要另加$228，計落，AA制都係每人$114，成餐計埋加一每人唔使$400，攞張五百蚊大牛出嚟仲有得找！牛角仲好抵死咁話，記得帶埋「真．戀人」一齊食，抽得靚！"},{"pid":"9a6986071fd00ca1daefdf74dc61f4dbdf52a61e","tid":216374,"uid":58147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:31:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"169bef64d7cd85a298c99734fbb1196fe0c29c3a","tid":216374,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":